================
description
================

1) This program accept directory name from user, from that directory it takes information 
	of all regular file and write it into another file, (named as "output_Info") and then
	read the whole contents from that output file.
2) Required directory_file name will be taken from command line

================
about the code
================

	input	:	directory name
	output	:	result - "output_Info" (regular) file.
 			
=============
How to run
=============

	make	:	compile the code and generates executable file as "myexe"
	make run:	run the executable with command line argument
			for this you have to pass parameter as: 
			
			$ make run p="parameter_value" 
	
=============
NOTE
=============

	1)If the given directory_file is unable to open, it will display the appropriate reason.
	2)"output_Info" file gets created by programatically.
